				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\alpha $$\end{document}, the second vector the k common independent variables, depicted by the coefficients βnk\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
